opencsd
------------------------------------------
CoreSight trace stream decoder developed openly

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libopencsd1-1.8.3-1bl1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Linaro/OpenCSD

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Linaro/OpenCSD/archive/refs/tags/v1.8.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack opencsd-1.8.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./opencsd-1.8.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/opencsd-1.8.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/opencsd-1.8.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsd1-1.8.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsd-devel-1.8.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

